PS Which other groups do you do PR for?

Suggested statement / response

Lucy

Further to your enquiry below I can confirm that as we had not committed 
cargoes to the vessel prior to the incident we are not looking for extra 
shipping capacity at this time. The extent in delay in delivery is unknown 
until a full assessment of the repairs required is completed.  It is 
important to note that although Enron has a Charter on the vessel we have not 
yet been delivered under that charter as it was still undergoing 
refurbishment by the Owner at the time of the fire.  Should you wish to 
enquire about the statues of the vessel, please call the owner directly.


